snippet: The Houston Dynamo are the latest team in Major League Soccer to open a new building, the 22,000-seat, $95 million BBVA Compass Stadium.
lead_paragraph: The Houston Dynamo are the latest team in Major League Soccer to open a new building, the 22,000-seat, $95 million BBVA Compass Stadium.

headline.seo: M.L.S. Keeps Moving Up as Houston Dynamo Open Stadium
headline.main: M.L.S. Continues to Bolster Growing Brand With New Stadium in Houston
